snippet.title: LES MILLS  BODYCOMBAT | Meta Quest
snippet.description:
Ready to experience BODYCOMBAT in a new way?

We’re entering the metaverse with the BODYCOMBAT VR app which is now available on the Quest platform. Dive into the world of VR with an Oculus Quest 2 headset, Rachael Newsham, and Dan Cohen to experience BODYCOMBAT like you never have before. An extensive workout portfolio, top quality coaching, innovative mechanics, and different intensities for all audiences is waiting for you.

Learn more at:  http://www.lesmills.com/bodycombat-vr/
 
Buy the experience at: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/4015163475201433

Join our Discord community: https://discord.gg/dtThPtTgx7

Join our Facebook community: https://www.facebook.com/groups/1770843376435250


_________________

The world’s best music, best moves, and best instructors. We bring it all together to create life-changing fitness experiences, powered by science.

Work out at a gym near you or whenever, wherever with LES MILLS+ https://lmod.co/onlineworkouts

Les Mills workouts:
https://www.lesmills.com/workouts

Find us on social:
https://www.instagram.com/lesmills
https://www.tiktok.com/@lesmills
https://www.facebook.com/lesmills
